1 Tuner + 1 or more non-Tuner monstersIf this card is Synchro Summoned using a non-Tuner Normal Monster(s) as a Synchro Material: You can activate this effect; this turn, it is unaffected by other card effects. If this card is Synchro Summoned using a non-Tuner Effect Monster(s) as a Synchro Material: You can target 1 other face-up card on the field; negate its effects. If this card is Synchro Summoned using a non-Tuner Pendulum Monster(s) as a Synchro Material: You can take control of 1 monster your opponent controls (their choice), but it cannot attack this turn.
